{"tid":1646080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《衰仔樂園》最新一集再X中国","createTime":"2019-10-11T06:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T01:56:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"79625a463cd134a72eecf1081c657b2da76e85d8","tid":1646080,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:54:41.000Z","msg":"風波再延燒，知名美國成人動畫《南方四賤客》（South Park）喜歡玩時事梗，影集推出至今每集幾乎都會酸爆全世界各個國家，最近剛好在劇集中播出有中國勞改營強迫勞動的橋段、大玩小熊維尼梗被封殺，但動畫似乎不畏風波，在最新的23季第3集中，再度大嗆中國政府，甚至飆髒話。<br />\n<br />\n其實美國成人動畫劇 《南方四賤客》時常針對各國進行黑色幽默諷刺拍攝，但最近剛好在劇集中影射有勞改營強迫勞動的橋段，惹惱中國遭到陸方封殺，隨後更發表超諷刺的道歉聲明，聲稱「我們也是愛錢超過愛民主與自由，習主席一點也不像小熊維尼。」目前大陸網站上已看不到《南方四賤客》大部分的劇集。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8zYbco6EKkWYoX__GZ.Pow--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg0/https://media.zenfs.com/en/setn.com.tw/75f3292bef83283e96881482fbdf8cde\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8zYbco6EKkWYoX__GZ.Pow--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F75f3292bef83283e96881482fbdf8cde&h=34411b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但劇組似乎毫不畏懼惹惱陸方，在最新的第23季第3集中再度撿到槍，這集「SHOTS!!!」當中描述，其中一位主角屎蛋（Stan）的父親蘭迪（Randy）原本要到中國販賣毒品，但夥伴不領情，隨後蘭迪將夥伴Towelie載到一處空地。<br />\n<br />\n動畫中蘭迪跟夥伴Towelie說：「我把你帶來這邊是為了道歉。」夥伴接著相當氣憤地說「No More Kissing China's Ass」（別再抱中國大腿）、自己從不想在中國政府監控的企業底下工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/m2_6zDaaB8PS1cQfmvo1nQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NTA0/https://media.zenfs.com/en/setn.com.tw/9d6f475b73a023bc5275ed9ae573b612\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fm2_6zDaaB8PS1cQfmvo1nQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NTA0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F9d6f475b73a023bc5275ed9ae573b612&h=41315b89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但蘭迪卻開始幫中國說話表示「他們是個愛好自由的國家」，最終為了要挽回夥伴Towelie才終於承諾不會在中國做生意，伙伴卻要藍迪罵髒話「去*的中國政府」，兩人這才終於和好。<br />\n<br />\n上一集酸味滿滿，這一集則是直接開嗆，雖然南方四賤客從未針對任何一個國家，而是到處以全世界的國家為主題，用黑色幽默手法呈現，但這回偏偏是影射大陸，勢必又要引發一陣討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%9B%E8%B3%A4%E5%AE%A2%E6%96%B0%E7%89%87%E5%86%8D%E9%96%8B%E9%85%B8-%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A3%86%E9%AB%92%E8%A9%B1-061025253.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25B3%25A4%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%2586%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2585%25B8-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A3%2586%25E9%25AB%2592%25E8%25A9%25B1-061025253.html&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwckXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=c9978b68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%9B%E8%B3%A4%E5%AE%A2%E6%96%B0%E7%89%87%E5%86%8D%E9%96%8B%E9%85%B8-%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A3%86%E9%AB%92%E8%A9%B1-061025253.html</a>"},{"pid":"1d4dd1ca7ee3c9e3e3438720e7ec28e5ac685307","tid":1646080,"uid":23023,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"會唔會搞到成個season 23 都係fuck the Chinese government<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62eb31f644cfa171ce328753cc4623e7e3a2e50","tid":1646080,"uid":320135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T07:00:34.000Z","msg":"做翻譯嗰位巴打會唔會翻譯埋呢集<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e786528fa62c41e51a7f2f66164de99b6f24a0","tid":1646080,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9823b8278a758b63d3c077af67ab73ff38ae5741","tid":1646080,"uid":235437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T08:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多咪再出多篇道歉文囉 are we okay now ? China <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.g